Claudia Schiffer builds Honduras mansion - reports . German supermodel Claudia Schiffer has built a mansion on the Honduran island of Roatan , local media said on Thursday . National newspapers said Schiffer spent $ 2 million for a new home on one of the exclusive Bay Islands off the Caribbean coast of Honduras . Local media also reported Schiffer and her husband , magician David Copperfield , would soon throw a party to open the house . The guest list was reported to include Hollywood stars Richard Gere and George Hamilton . But Roatan Mayor Ricardo Merren was highly sceptical , the reports said . " It ' s not true . We all know each other here , and we would know if it were true , " Merren was quoted as saying . 
